Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,早~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,雫 这个家里果然有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,半夜睡不着时醒来就看到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,枕头前站着个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,眼瞪瞪地俯视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我喜欢戳破蛋黄的煎蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,话又说来 大叔你跟雫一点都不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我说…你怎么能这么平常心？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\pos(898,658)}放暑假
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你这货又得补习了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田竟然是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里搞错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假先彻底预习一遍好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 好啦 打起精神来啊 小水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,689分很高分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,像我全部科目加起来都没300分…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一定又要补考了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我 比较喜欢比基尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,阿春 好大胆！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我不清楚你在想什么 但我是不会去海边的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你们要报名球技大会的项目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 小水你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我对答案有疑问 要去问清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她就没想过享受下学校的活动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都有我这个朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,估计她没把你当朋友来看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,{\frz8.195\pos(656,78)\c&H3F3C3D&\bord0\shad0}请在50字以内简述主人公的此时心情。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968,556)\bord0\shad0\frz10.75\c&H444444&}放走金龟婿 对人生绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这题批三角（不全对）了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天已经收摊了  老师不想回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是你的值班时间 请你老实工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不是答错 但是也不是正确答案 所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以为什…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要说为什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这答案一点都表达不出失恋的痛苦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何也得不到回应的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,心碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24}<Heart Break>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别了 我的爱情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 就是你被人甩了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的个人的观念 我无法认同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,给我正经点干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,水谷同学还没有体会到恋爱那种煎熬的滋味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,说来 我被阿春甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让阿春再喜欢上我后 再来告白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎样让他喜欢上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说到头 我到底是怎么喜欢上阿春的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,加分了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是吉田春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 包心菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 对 对不起~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,被死瞪着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要老瞪着人看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哈啊 我才没有瞪着人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,人家就是因为这个原因避开你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕别人 别人也怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我蛮喜欢阿春笑着的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,干烧虾仁 干烧虾仁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,额 吉田春…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我蛮喜欢阿春笑着的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,蛮喜欢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,蛮喜欢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,蛮喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,蛮喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,蛮…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.15,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,昨天的特别节目看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:23.94,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 东西掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:24.99,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 谢…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那个交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我来搬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不害怕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他好帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是只公鸡 名字叫名古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 破冰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,阿春本来就长得很帅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,最近开始待人也亲切了 女生当然都心动了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,果然跟雫说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不瞪着人看后就开始有人来套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是眼睛的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.64,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,阿春同学 阿春同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.20,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,教我们功课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:27.27,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,谁管你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.92,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,你们不会自己做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.39,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,呀啊~好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,说话的态度跟之前没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是一旦破冰后就说什么都能接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.75,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,我哪里可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.45,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,阿春同学 真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:36.71,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,一点都不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,来找宠物消散寂寞的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 夏目同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为事实就是如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,阿春最近都被女生围着没法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,传回来 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,直接射门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田 你都踢反球门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,反了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:06.99,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,阿春同学 看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大家的反应变化真是太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,前阵子都还是谁都不敢接近他来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧 得去练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦呀 哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 小水 你吃醋了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这 就是吃醋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她好坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.52,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(646,84)}全天球技大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.52,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,426)}加油 B班！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.52,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1264,76)}夺取冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 小水 你完全没有碰到球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你对我那么说我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到夏目同学会是运动型的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 情况怎样了？女子排球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果小水能再动一下的话还是有办法取胜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这边吉田可是超活跃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他热血过头打了裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 阿春呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田能这样持续下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,之前不是有说过一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田初中的时候就不来上学过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一年级开学的时候发生了群架事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,事情闹得很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,额 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那家伙看起来真的很可怕 所以周围的人也都缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,之后 吉田开始不来上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这次希望能持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都有过去嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么阿佐同学会那么在意阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为之前你们都没说过话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我欠他人情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么味的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,老师叫我们得去准备下节课的工具…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？到时间了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那我一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是同班同学 但是我们都没怎么交流过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.04,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,比赛打的漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 还是叫老师来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真是疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你在往人家头上砸什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 都长头包了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,日 够了 不需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我认识你 之前闯入C班的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,揍了女生还害人家流鼻血的事是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,流鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太嚣张了 一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么非得被你这混蛋说「不需要」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 干架了干架了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不妙啊 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 够了吧 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你们都在做什么啊喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- -摔倒了……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,唉哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真是搞不懂 明明是好心帮忙却又把事情搞大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到我竟然也沦落到逃避老师的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我 做错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,之前也发生过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,回过神来 周围都用奇怪的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是完全搞不懂为啥会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法说你的做法就是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阿春是很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:14:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 阿春是很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,终有一天 大家会明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的雫像个英雄似的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄是在别人危急的时候登场的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,危急的是对方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,额头 弄花了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,下场比赛开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,再 再见了 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果比赛赢了 暑假一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,加 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,最后 阿春赢了这个不算赌局的赌局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:36.73,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,夏目朝子要从这么高开始起跳了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:38.26,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:43.26,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,2号 吉田春 要从更高的地方起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.49,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,好耶~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.15,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,夏天啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那么今天就照顾新人 钓鲑鱼和鳟鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼儿们都会盯着在上流的钓饵的 所以要从上流往下放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,游泳的时候就抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你是野人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 夏目妹妹 能帮洗下这个锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不错嘛 溪钓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 小满跟阿春是表兄弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 这家伙的老爹是我老妈的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然后高中距离我家比较近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今年开始在我家住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.10,Default Upper,,0,0,0,,哦 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小水 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你是亲哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不是不是 他老哥另有其人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,说到他老哥嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小满
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快起来 到店里了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要卸行李 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫醒阿春了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他睡得真熟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我开始分手信 大家在店里等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好的~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,说来最近我建了个论坛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真伤人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一看见人家就立马逃跑 太大惊小怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,阿阿阿佐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是之前的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,跟小满哥要钱的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 刚刚阿春突然跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 满善 人家以为我向你讹钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是阿春的哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是吉田优山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,阿春承蒙大家照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 这家伙就是今天跟你们说的阿春的老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 跟他借钱的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你切开了吗 我还想玩打西瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,才不玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 没想到阿春竟然还有你们这样的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样 他还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏水谷同学 他也都来学校上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也不全是我的功劳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他是个笨蛋 但请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 阿春为什么要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那个吗 这很平常啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他有严重的兄控情结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,说是吉田的哥哥 还以为是个什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到人蛮好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要去买东西 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,雫妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今后 阿春就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢 是个奇怪的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然比不上他弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么老做这种把人吓破胆的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起玩打西瓜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这人难道到现在都在苦恼这个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,手 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥哥说 你有严重的兄控情结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要躲开你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我讨厌他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你好烦啊 不要什么都追根究底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是生气回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我家也有西瓜 要打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 打开了哦 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得自己比较了解他了 但又发现对他一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要什么都追根究底
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什么让他露出那么可怕的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 刚刚对你说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都是雫来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,得做点什么报答下你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,约会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:21:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就用约会来报答我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那也行…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,说来 这老感觉不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,打西瓜都是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道的事情 等到能知道的那天便好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,事情就只是这样
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,吉田 一对上镜头就异常紧张 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是只公鸡吗
